These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, indie, hip-hop, techno
1. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of techno##1
2. the fan of indie is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
3. the fan of d&b is on the right of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | indie | d&b | techno |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different pets are kept: hamster, rabbit, snake, hedgehog
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the hamster is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | hamster | snake | rabbit | hedgehog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, cooking, video-games, gardening
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby   | video-games | traveling | cooking | gardening |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, snowmobile, helicopter, bus
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |    3    |  4  |
| Transport   | helicopter | scooter | snowmobile | bus |

 #################################

 
