.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, crime, superhero, mystery
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
3. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3       |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | superhero | crime | fantasy |

