2. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
3. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |   3    |     4     |
| Food   | strawberry | cranberry | blueberry | cherry |

